  "_notes": [
    "All ObjectId parameters must be valid MongoDB ObjectIds (24 hex characters)",
    "All dates should be ISO 8601 strings or Date objects",
    "Query parameters for date filtering: year (4 digits), month (1-12)",
    "Error responses follow format: { success: false, error: string, code?: string, details?: array }",
    "Success responses follow format: { success: true, data: any, count?: number }",
    "Rate fields (base_rate, op_rate, clean_rate, sub_clean_rate, demand_rate) accept numbers and are automatically converted to strings for storage",
    "Drop status changes automatically update item statuses: 'upcoming' → items become 'pending', 'active' → items become 'available'"
  ]
